00:53:31,720 --> 00:53:35,560
- Don't apologise.
- I don't like him driving at night.

765
00:53:35,640 --> 00:53:39,880
Stanley, I'm so sorry about this,
but I have to get these papers.

766
00:53:39,960 --> 00:53:42,440
- Would you like some company?
- No, not at all.

767
00:53:42,520 --> 00:53:45,160
- Darling, forgive me.
- Chris will take you.

768
00:53:45,240 --> 00:53:49,280
It was a wonderful evening,
and if you're here when I get back...

769
00:53:49,360 --> 00:53:51,640
- Thank you.
- Don't worry. We're fine.

770
00:53:51,720 --> 00:53:58,000
I do apologise. Let's just finish the coffee,
sit down and... he'll be back.

771
00:56:04,000 --> 00:56:06,000
