772
00:56:06,080 --> 00:56:08,840
The eyes of God see all.

773
00:56:09,480 --> 00:56:13,880
Listen to me, Judah. There is
absolutely nothing that escapes his sight.

774
00:56:13,960 --> 00:56:17,040
He sees the righteous
and he sees the wicked.

775
00:56:17,120 --> 00:56:19,480
And the righteous will be rewarded,

776
00:56:19,560 --> 00:56:22,120
but the wicked will be punished

777
00:56:22,200 --> 00:56:24,200
for eternity.

778
00:57:44,880 --> 00:57:46,680
Hello?

