897
01:05:35,280 --> 01:05:37,280
An inert object.

898
01:05:38,360 --> 01:05:41,720
There was nothing behind her eyes
if you looked into them.

899
01:05:41,800 --> 01:05:44,400
All you saw was a

900
01:05:44,480 --> 01:05:46,480
black void.

901
01:06:21,280 --> 01:06:23,480
Can I help you?

902
01:06:25,120 --> 01:06:27,720
