903
01:06:27,800 --> 01:06:29,800
Really? When?

904
01:06:30,680 --> 01:06:32,680
Many years ago.

905
01:06:34,200 --> 01:06:37,440
My brother and I
used to race through these rooms.

906
01:06:38,480 --> 01:06:42,880
He was a wonderful kid, my brother.
We were very close in those days.

907
01:06:45,920 --> 01:06:50,560
My father had high hopes for him,
but it never seemed to... work out for him.

908
01:06:54,960 --> 01:06:57,200
Would you mind if I just take a minute?

909
01:06:57,280 --> 01:07:00,440
Everything seems to be
flooding through me.

910
01:07:00,520 --> 01:07:02,520
Sure.

911
01:07:22,680 --> 01:07:25,200
Come on, Sol. Get on with it. I'm hungry.

912
